     </div>\n          </div>\n\n    <div class=\"box box0 box2 aos-init aos-animate\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n       \n         <h3 class=\"h3-5 flex\"></h3>\n                <div class=\"arc-con arc-cons1\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">Professor, <a href=\"http://iiis.tsinghua.edu.cn/en\">Institute for Interdisciplinary Information Sciences</a> (IIIS, headed by Prof. <a href=\"yaoqizhi.htm\">Andrew Yao</a>), Tsinghua University.</p>\n<p><strong> </strong><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://people.iiis.tsinghua.edu.cn/~jianli/paper-date.htm\">Publications </a>(full list in <a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=zX7i1EkAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Google Scholar</a>)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://people.iiis.tsinghua.edu.cn/~jianli/talks.htm\">Some Talks (with slides)</a></p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\"><a href=\"https://people.iiis.tsinghua.edu.cn/~jianli/ADLgroup-mem.htm\">Research Group</a></p>\n</div></div>\n \n  </div>\n  \n    <div class=\"box box0 box3 aos-init\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n       \n         <h3 class=\"h3-5 flex\"><img src=\"../../images/h3-5.png\" alt=\"\">Research Interests</h3>\n                <div class=\"arc-con arc-cons1\"><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\">\n <li><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">Theoretical Computer Science (Approximation Algorithms, Computational Geometry, Stochastic Combinatorial Optimization)</p></li>\n <li><p>Machine Learning (Learning Theory, Machine Learning for Tabular/Time series/Spatial-temporal data, Large generative models)</p></li>\n <li><p>ML and Finance <a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/intro-to-quant\">机器学习与量化投资 知乎专栏</a>（由我们组同学维护）</p></li>\n <li><p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">Large-scale Data Management and Analytics (Databases, Crowdsourcing)</p></li>\n</ul></div>\n \n  </div>\n  \n    <div class=\"box box0 box3 aos-init\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n       \n         <h3 class=\"h3-5 flex\"><img src=\"../../images/h3-5.png\" alt=\"\">Professional Services</h3>\n                <div class=\"arc-con arc-cons1\"><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\">\n <li><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\"><b>PC members </b>: SODA 2025, TAMC 2023, IJTCS 2022 (PC co-chair), AAAI 2022 (senior PC), IJCAI 2022 (senior PC), <a href=\"https://conf.ccf.org.cn/web/html5/index.html?globalId=m8266084332843868161617120408137&amp;type=1\">全国理论计算机年会 NCTCS 2021</a> (PC co-chair),IJTCS 2021, <a href=\"https://econcs.pku.edu.cn/ijtcs2020/IJTCS2020.html\"> IJTCS 2020</a> (PC co-chair), IJCAI 2021(area chair), AAAI 2021(senior PC), ACML 2021 (senior PC), IJCAI 2020 (AI-in-Fintech Track), <a href=\"http://tamc2020.csu.edu.cn/\">TAMC 2020</a>, <a href=\"https://icml.cc/Conferences/2020/Dates\">ICML 2020</a>, <a href=\"https://socg20.inf.ethz.ch/\">SoCG2020</a>, <a href=\"https://aaai.org/Conferences/AAAI-20/\">AAAI 2020</a>, <a href=\"https://people.iiis.tsinghua.edu.cn/~jianli/FAW2019/FAW2019.html\">FAW 2019</a>, <a href=\"https://dasfaa2019.eng.cmu.ac.th/\">DASFAA 2019</a>, AAAI 18, NIPS17, <a href=\"https://2017.icml.cc/\">ICML17</a>(PC reviewer), WAOA17, AAAI17, <a href=\"http://icml.cc/2016/\">ICML2016</a>(PC reviewer), <a href=\"http://icde2016.fi/\">ICDE2016</a>, <a href=\"http://www.easyconferences.eu/icalp2016/\">ICALP2016</a>, <a href=\"http://www.cs.sdu.edu.cn/waim2015/\">WAIM2015</a>, <a href=\"http://www.wi-opt.org/\">WiOpt2015</a>, <a href=\"http://www.cs.sdu.edu.cn/waim2015/\">WAIM2015 (proceeding chair)</a><strong>, </strong><a href=\"http://conference.iiis.tsinghua.edu.cn/CTW2014/\">China Theory Week 2014</a><strong> </strong>(co-chair), <a href=\"http://www.cis.umac.mo/waim2014/\">WAIM2014</a>, <a href=\"http://www.cs.gsu.edu/COCOON2014/\">COCOON2014</a>, <a href=\"http://www.cs.hku.hk/isaac2013/\">ISAAC2013</a>, <a href=\"http://www.cs.hku.hk/tamc2013/index.html\">TAMC2013</a>, <a href=\"http://www.cs.zju.edu.cn/algo/cocoon2013/\">COCOON2013</a>, <a href=\"http://www.cikm2012.org/index.php\">CIKM2012</a></p></li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\">\n <li><p